Pattern- Greedy

var minPatches = function(nums, n) {
    let miss = 1;
    let i = 0;
    let patches = 0;

    while (miss <= n) {
        if (i < nums.length && nums[i] <= miss) {
            miss += nums[i];
            i++;
        } else {
            miss += miss;
            patches++;
        }
    }

    return patches;
};




Key Idea
Track smallest missing number miss
Range [1, miss) is currently covered
If next number ≤ miss → extend range
Else → patch with miss
Core Insight
Adding miss doubles the reachable range
New range becomes [1, 2*miss)
